{"tid":1052130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不再堅持　「酷MA萌」官方中文名改為「熊本熊」","createTime":"2019-03-08T05:45:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T12:47:45.000Z","uid":75969,"like":139,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"68f9cb2beb22f0d15a7dc989c8c2844f21e5d99a","tid":1052130,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T05:45:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190307/640_93cd0e222af5689dbaf42b32e49fb62c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190307%2F640_93cd0e222af5689dbaf42b32e49fb62c.jpg&h=9eb56896&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">日本熊本縣吉祥物「酷MA萌」，19日將改名為大眾熟知的「熊本熊」。法新社</span><br />\n<br />\n日本熊本縣政府今天透露，計劃更改該縣吉祥物「酷MA萌」（くまモン，日語發音為kumamon）在台灣、香港和中國使用的官方中文名稱，從目前的「酷MA萌」改為「熊本熊」。<br />\n<br />\n共同社今天報導，此舉旨在強調這是熊本的吉祥物。熊本縣已就「熊本熊」這一名稱申請註冊商標，預定本月19日開始改變叫法。<br />\n<br />\n目前使用的「酷MA萌」與日語發音相似，有帥氣與可愛的含義。然而華人遊客卻不這麼認為。熊本縣相關負責人近年努力推廣酷MA萌這個官方名稱，但顯然仍改變不了華人遊客的既定印象，如今順應潮流改名為大眾較為熟知的「熊本熊」。<br />\n<br />\n「酷MA萌」在2010年誕生，熊本縣當初的角色設定「並不是熊」。隨著「酷MA萌」走紅，2013年熊本縣政府與上海事務所職員商討過後，正式將「酷MA萌」這個音譯定為官方中文名，官方周邊商品也一律使用「酷MA萌」這個名字，並在台灣、香港、中國、新加坡都申請了商標註冊，可是即使經過推廣，「酷MA萌」這個名字仍不及「熊本熊」普及。<br />\n<br />\n另外熊本縣政府也指出，<span style=\"color: red;\">發現中國有心人士鑽商標法漏洞，搶以「酷MA萌」申請商標註冊，導致濫用情況</span>，決定改名「熊本熊」，以防不正當使用。（國際中心／綜合外電報導） <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190307/640_dd726026aa2156c6476f11b7f5274e8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190307%2F640_dd726026aa2156c6476f11b7f5274e8d.jpg&h=c7147c1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">「酷MA萌」深受兒童喜愛。法新社<br />\n</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190307/1529109\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190307%2F1529109&d=fEJCtfATBeMWJ6YDVJZPMnlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=0e9a0a6b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190307%2F1529109&h=9f081942\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190307/1529109</a>"},{"pid":"cf8724989dba59c494e8439275cc44791eb31ca4","tid":1052130,"uid":167330,"like":331,"dislike":2,"score":329,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T05:48:07.000Z","msg":"但我不嬲都叫開熊本熊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea00dbcfdb4f2e8f2ec6416110d2d718829636a6","tid":1052130,"uid":75969,"like":172,"dislike":2,"score":170,"quote":{"pid":"cf8724989dba59c494e8439275cc44791eb31ca4","tid":1052130,"uid":167330,"like":331,"dislike":2,"score":329,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T05:48:07.000Z","msg":"但我不嬲都叫開熊本熊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T05:51:31.000Z","msg":"咪好似寵物小精靈同精靈寶可夢咁<br />\n不過熊本熊肯改返中文地區熟悉嘅名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6d389c052f860a1c40775990a75b2d1bac5348a","tid":1052130,"uid":143499,"like":169,"dislike":2,"score":167,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T05:51:50.000Z","msg":"隻野真係好撚嬲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e710264d7bd1f39b06092e9b740d28c38ccc3cf0","tid":1052130,"uid":66324,"like":91,"dislike":5,"score":86,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T05:55:20.000Z","msg":"係老任先咁唔尊重其他地方"},{"pid":"bd560bfb31baa293ecb56c682e57bfd1f201d184","tid":1052130,"uid":165336,"like":128,"dislike":4,"score":124,"quote":{"pid":"e710264d7bd1f39b06092e9b740d28c38ccc3cf0","tid":1052130,"uid":66324,"like":91,"dislike":5,"score":86,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T05:55:20.000Z","msg":"係老任先咁唔尊重其他地方"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T05:58:24.000Z","msg":"而家佢都係為支那同台灣,唔係為香港,<br />\n只不過咁岩香港人都係叫佢做熊本熊咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪自作多情啦,商業考慮一定係支那先,<br />\n支那唔得就台灣,幾時輪到香港人口小又孤鳩寒<img src=\"/ass